import { Button, TextField } from "@mui/material";
import React from "react";

export default function Login() {
    return (
        <form noValidate autoComplete="off">
            <TextField 
            label="Email"
            name="email"
            variant="outlined"
            />
            <TextField 
            label="Name"
            name="name"
            variant="outlined"
            />
            <Button 
            type ="submit"
            variant="outlined"
            size="large">Start</Button>
        </form>
    )
}
